title: Ebro In The Morning - Chappelle Comedy Brawl + Does Sean Paul Know White Ish?
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 5/4/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about Reproductive Rights being in danger, Dave Chappelle being attacked, and Sean Paul plays White Ish Wednesday! 

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems and get the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
